en_question:
    A company has 4 thousand yuan in capital and can invest in three projects: A, B, and C. The benefit values corresponding to different investment amounts for each project are shown in Table 7-18. How should the funds be allocated to maximize the total benefit(in thousand yuan)? Formulate and solve the mathematical model.

\begin{table}[h]
    \centering
    \caption{Benefit values for different investment amounts (Table 7-18)}
    \renewcommand{\arraystretch}{1.2}
    \begin{tabular}{c|ccccc}
        \toprule
        Project & \multicolumn{5}{c}{Investment Amount (thousand yuan)} \\
        \cmidrule(lr){2-6}
        & 0 & 1 & 2 & 3 & 4 \\
        \midrule
        A & 0 & 41 & 48 & 60 & 66 \\
        B & 0 & 42 & 50 & 60 & 66 \\
        C & 0 & 64 & 68 & 78 & 76 \\
        \bottomrule
    \end{tabular}
\end{table}

cn_question:
    某公司有资金 4 万元，可向 A、B、C 三个项目投资，已知各项目不同投资额的相应效益值如表 7-18 所示，问如何分配资金可使总效益最大。列出数学模型求解。

\begin{table}[h]
    \centering
    \caption{不同投资额对应效益值（表 7-18）}
    \renewcommand{\arraystretch}{1.2}
    \begin{tabular}{c|ccccc}
        \toprule
        项目 & \multicolumn{5}{c}{投资额（万元）} \\
        \cmidrule(lr){2-6}
        & 0 & 1 & 2 & 3 & 4 \\
        \midrule
        A & 0 & 41 & 48 & 60 & 66 \\
        B & 0 & 42 & 50 & 60 & 66 \\
        C & 0 & 64 & 68 & 78 & 76 \\
        \bottomrule
    \end{tabular}
\end{table}
